Under the epidemic, a lot of parents stay at home, with a child spent a long winter vacation.

Suspended without suspension, the teacher when the anchor, Internet classes at home, but many parents straight ho-live. While working from home, but also to participate in the school layout of the task, the daily broadcast classes alone fancy punch card, drove a number of parents crazy.

Parents now do not understand, clearly delayed the beginning of school, but their own more busy.

Live

On February 10, primary and secondary schools across the country began online classes. On the same day alone, 600,000 teachers in more than 300 cities across the country turned into anchorpersons and used some software to give students live lessons.

"I buy, this problem really well do head Oh! All the students, quick, give me to learn him! " Watching live class taste, can be very different from watching live shopping, parents soon enough.

Although it is home class, but early reading, raising the national flag, eye exercises do not fall. Parents need to take pictures, punch in and out of their children 24 hours a day, otherwise EITE, the head teacher, will have a private chat with you.

Look at the national flag after writing, parents have to participate, the teacher said clearly, after watching must have parents'feelings.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Screenshot of parental notification group

Of course, usually not without a variety of written, oral work, on-line as well.

After the notice was issued, the school arranged a series of child discipline, in the form of competitions from Labor, Handwork, sports, reading and other tasks, asking parents to complete.

Parents often complain about "Wechat Homework" , but as soon as they hear that the children are going to be evaluated, they immediately start a carp fight and roll up their sleeves.

Parents at this time Meng ran found that the start of class family is an extension of the classroom, open a live class, the living room has become a classroom, with their children in school.

If you're a full-time parent, you might be able to handle it, but most parents work from home. I can't go to class with my kid, and I can't go to work with you.

When you have to concentrate on responding to the boss's message, the baby jumping noisy, one moment drilling you, the other moment your head, you dare not angry on both sides.

A parent laments that children are the biggest obstacle to working from home. The biggest challenge of working from home is not that co-ordination tools don't work, nor that remote communication is inefficient, but that children don't go to school.

The wrong way

It's a long vacation, so it's a good time to child discipline. Paying attention to students'life, life, survival and other education during holidays is a more suitable education for students at present.

##The Ministry of Education also said that "no suspension" does not refer to online classes in the pure sense, nor does it refer only to the study of school courses, but rather to a broad sense of study, as long as the content and methods that help students grow and progress are available.

Home-based learning has its own advantages, parents can be combined with epidemic prevention and control, to tell children some of the epidemic resistance war emerged in the advanced deeds, promote the virtues of society. Also can let the children read some classics famous piece more, edify sentiment.

However, parents have found that home-based learning is intended to completely replace classroom instruction, regardless of the differences in learning outcomes between home-based learning and classroom instruction due to objective conditions and students'ability to learn autonomously.

What's more, there are different age groups for online classes. Pupils do not have to rush to learn new content, the effect is difficult to ensure, and long-term staring at electronic screens seriously affect vision.

The Ministry of Education has also pointed out that there is no uniform mandatory requirement for online learning in the lower grades of primary school, leaving the choice to parents and students. At the same time, students must not be forced to go online every day, "clock in" , upload learning video and so on, to prevent the increase of unnecessary burden.

A while ago the most let the parents laugh and cry is, according to the past time calculate actually has not opened the school, the children instead all attend the class.

Since the introduction of live courses, students have started online courses in the new semester ahead of the official start date planned everywhere.

Some education experts have pointed out that the "suspension without suspension" at this stage is a substitution of concepts and a violation of regulations to make up lessons, causing a great deal of excitement and mobilization of all teachers, students (including kindergarten children) , parents, have suffered a lot of abuse.

Long

Suffering, suffering, child school days more and more distant.

The Ministry of Education issued a notice on January 27th, asking that the spring term of 2020 be postponed. Since then, provinces across the country have postponed the original start time.

Parents in Jiangsu and Shanghai saw the start of school delayed until Feb. 17. A few days later, the school day was postponed again, and the school day was postponed until the end of February.

Since February 5, Shanghai, Zhejiang, Jiangsu, Chongqing, Guangdong and Anhui have announced that schools at all levels will not open until the end of February, and Inner Mongolia, Gansu, Heilongjiang, Tibet and Qinghai are expected to open in early March, hubei, Jilin, Tianjin, Beijing, Ningxia, Shanxi, Xinjiang and other provinces have no specific starting date.

It's tough for kids, too. They know they can't stay home for more than a week. Within a week, clothes to hand rice to mouth, not satisfied can also say that you two mouth, is living a fairy life.

As long as after a week, the mother saw in the morning did not get up, without a word straight off the quilt. After dinner, a look let to wash the dishes. I checked his eyes. You are his mother.

Now that school is starting later, some parents are still working from home, and at Hitotsu Yane no Shita, the whole family is too lazy to look at each other twice, after all, is too disgusted.

That's not all. Some parents were surprised to hear that the gym teacher had begun live-streaming Homework assignments, such as rope skipping. As everyone can not go out, the parents had to take the baby on the balcony jump, jump to all the neighbors began to dislike each other.

Fortunately, many parents are not far from work, watching the day to return to work is close, close, really close. If we keep this up, we're GONNA end up in psych.

Bringing a baby makes parents desperate, and I've never been so desperate to get to work.
